---
import { COMPANY_SERVICES } from "../../consts";
---

<section class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900">
  <div class="py-8 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl lg:py-16 lg:px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-md text-center mb-8 lg:mb-16">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        Layanan kotacom.id
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 sm:text-xl dark:text-gray-400">
        kotacom.id menyediakan layanan lengkap IT Service, Pengadaan Hardware & Software, 
        Website Development, Software Development, Publications, dan Social Media Management 
        di wilayah Surabaya - Sidoarjo
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Services Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="flex justify-center items-center w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-300" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h10a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2.22l.123.489.804.804A1 1 0 0113 18H7a1 1 0 01-.707-1.707l.804-.804L7.22 15H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V5zm5.771 7H5V5h10v7H8.771z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ml-4 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">IT Service</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Pengadaan & Maintenance sistem IT, support teknis, dan infrastruktur teknologi untuk kebutuhan bisnis Anda.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="flex justify-center items-center w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 dark:text-green-300" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.316 3.051a1 1 0 01.633 1.265l-4 12a1 1 0 11-1.898-.632l4-12a1 1 0 011.265-.633zM5.707 6.293a1 1 0 010 1.414L3.414 10l2.293 2.293a1 1 0 11-1.414 1.414l-3-3a1 1 0 010-1.414l3-3a1 1 0 011.414 0zm8.586 0a1 1 0 011.414 0l3 3a1 1 0 010 1.414l-3 3a1 1 0 11-1.414-1.414L16.586 10l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ml-4 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Development</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Website & Software Development, aplikasi custom, dan sistem informasi sesuai kebutuhan spesifik perusahaan.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="flex justify-center items-center w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-300" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ml-4 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Publications</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Content & Social Media Management, publikasi digital, dan strategi komunikasi online untuk meningkatkan brand awareness.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="flex justify-center items-center w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-300" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h4a1 1 0 010 2H6.414l2.293 2.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L5 6.414V8a1 1 0 01-2 0V4zm9 1a1 1 0 010-2h4a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 01-2 0V6.414l-2.293 2.293a1 1 0 11-1.414-1.414L13.586 5H12zm-9 7a1 1 0 012 0v1.586l2.293-2.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L6.414 15H8a1 1 0 010 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-4zm13-1a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 01-1 1h-4a1 1 0 010-2h1.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 111.414-1.414L15.586 13H14a1 1 0 01-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ml-4 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Hardware & Software</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Penjualan dan pengadaan hardware komputer, software lisensi, dan solusi teknologi terkini untuk bisnis.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="flex justify-center items-center w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600 dark:text-red-300" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ml-4 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Konsultasi IT</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Konsultasi gratis untuk kebutuhan teknologi bisnis, analisis sistem, dan rekomendasi solusi IT terbaik.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="flex justify-center items-center w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.267 3.455a3.066 3.066 0 001.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 013.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 001.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 012.812 2.812c.051.643.304 1.254.723 1.745a3.066 3.066 0 010 3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723 1.745 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812 2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-3.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812-2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 010-3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 012.812-2.812zm7.44 5.252a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ml-4 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Support & Maintenance</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Layanan support berkelanjutan, maintenance sistem, troubleshooting, dan technical support 24/7 untuk bisnis Anda.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <p class="mb-6 text-lg text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        Tertarik dengan layanan kami? Hubungi tim ahli kotacom.id untuk konsultasi gratis
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/services"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-center text-white bg-blue-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-300 dark:bg-blue-600 dark:hover:bg-blue-700 dark:focus:ring-blue-800"
        >
          Lihat Semua Layanan
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://wa.me/085799520350"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-center text-white bg-green-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-green-700 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-green-300 dark:bg-green-600 dark:hover:bg-green-700 dark:focus:ring-green-800"
        >
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M7.978 4a2.553 2.553 0 0 0-1.926.877C4.233 6.7 3.699 8.751 4.153 10.814c.44 1.995 1.778 3.893 3.456 5.572 1.68 1.679 3.577 3.018 5.57 3.459 2.062.456 4.115-.073 5.94-1.885a2.556 2.556 0 0 0 .001-3.861l-1.21-1.21a2.689 2.689 0 0 0-3.802 0l-.617.618a.806.806 0 0 1-1.14 0l-1.854-1.855a.807.807 0 0 1 0-1.14l.618-.62a2.692 2.692 0 0 0 0-3.803l-1.21-1.211A2.555 2.555 0 0 0 7.978 4Z"></path>
          </svg>
          Konsultasi via WhatsApp
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>